name: Crypto AI
description: What is the project about? Crypto AI, an AI-powered using AI Machine Learning to Create Digital Asset. What makes your project unique? Two working product - AI Artist: https://cai.codes/artist and AI Chat - https://cai.codes/chat History of your project. Development of Image Diffusion trained to invert CLIP image embeddings. We finetuned SD 2.1 to accept a CLIP ViT-L/14 image embedding in addition to the text encodings. This means that the model can be used to produce image variations, but can also be combined with a text-to-image embedding prior to yield a full text-to-image model at 768x768 resolution.
